"{\"uid\": \"tsn.ca-olympics-melissa-humana-paredes-brandie-wilkerson-earn-silver-for-canada-in-beach-volleyball-1.2160430\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published:August 09, 2024 at 5:33PM EDT  PARIS - Canada's remarkable run to the beach volleyball final at the Paris Games ended with a match that had it all.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 49, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.999997655301306, \"rank\": 2.284803252517809e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only thing missing for Brandie Wilkerson and Melissa Humana-Paredes was a victory.\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 186, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandie_Wilkerson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brandie Wilkerson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandie_Wilkerson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandie_Wilkerson\"}, {\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Humana-Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Toronto duo dropped a 2-1 (26-24, 12-21, 15-10) decision to Brazil on Friday but still became the first Canadian women to reach the Olympic podium in the sport.\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 251, \"end\": 258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 0.9034818910170539, \"rank\": 0.1057773204711326, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}, {\"begin\": 311, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9986960000473794, \"rank\": 0.0013056943257172245, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9997857356551872, \"rank\": 0.0002143102518270616, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The silver medal came after a 1-2 start in pool play and qualification via a lucky-loser match earlier in the tournament.\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We showed a lot of people what's possible,\\\" Humana-Paredes said.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 581, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Humana-Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And we showed a lot of people what just pure heart and grit and the intangibles of sport means.\\\"\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gold-medal match featured multiple set points, great rallies, a tiebreaker - even an on-court dust-up - before Ana Patricia Ramos and Eduarda Santos (Duda) Lisboa nailed down their first Olympic title.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the loss, the Canadians were beaming after their history-making run at Eiffel Tower Stadium.\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The only other Canadian medal was a men's bronze at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9997857356551872, \"rank\": 0.0002143102518270616, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 1089, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999996891524944, \"rank\": 2.520365046748116e-07, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am absolutely thrilled to make history in Canada for beach volleyball,\\\" Wilkerson said.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.999997655301306, \"rank\": 2.284803252517809e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's something that's keeping my head held high.\\\"\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada charged out to an 8-2 lead as the top-ranked Brazilians seemed unsettled.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1244, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.999997655301306, \"rank\": 2.284803252517809e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1296, \"end\": 1306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999031388, \"rank\": 9.706457098100313e-11, \"text\": \"Brazilians\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Ramos block - complete with finger wag - cut the Canadian lead to five at 13-8.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9997857356551872, \"rank\": 0.0002143102518270616, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both teams had set points but Brazil converted on its fourth opportunity.\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9986960000473794, \"rank\": 0.0013056943257172245, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the second set, Humana-Paredes made a dig and followed with an emphatic conversion to give Canada an 11-10 lead entering the technical timeout.\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Humana-Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\"}, {\"begin\": 1577, \"end\": 1583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.999997655301306, \"rank\": 2.284803252517809e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada continued to apply pressure thanks to its strong defensive effort and effective net play.\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.999997655301306, \"rank\": 2.284803252517809e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Humana-Paredes ace made it 18-11 and Canada rolled into the tiebreaker.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Humana-Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\"}, {\"begin\": 1767, \"end\": 1773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.999997655301306, \"rank\": 2.284803252517809e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil responded early in the decider and led 12-7 in the first-to-15 set.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1803, \"end\": 1809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9986960000473794, \"rank\": 0.0013056943257172245, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tensions rose though when Wilkerson saw her family members in the stands and was \\\"cheering at them\\\" after earning the point.\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ramos took exception and all four players started jawing at each other across the net.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2004, \"end\": 2009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\", \"score\": 0.9999999714405026, \"rank\": 2.338120157056417e-08, \"text\": \"Ramos\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The on-court referee got in the middle of the altercation to keep things from escalating.\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She thought I was cheering at her, but I was looking past her,\\\" Wilkerson said, calling it a miscommunication that was hugged out after the match.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The on-site DJ got in on the fun by playing John Lennon's \\\"Imagine\\\" on the loudspeakers.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2375, \"end\": 2386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\", \"score\": 0.999998131337106, \"rank\": 1.8686662682051743e-06, \"text\": \"John Lennon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The players eventually smiled and the sellout crowd lapped it up.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They played the song, which was hilarious,\\\" said Wilkerson, who was given a yellow card.\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it was just a moment for everyone to take a breath and reset.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it worked to our advantage.\\\"\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada chipped away at the deficit but Brazil eventually took control and completed the win on the second match point.\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2686, \"end\": 2692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.999997655301306, \"rank\": 2.284803252517809e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2725, \"end\": 2731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9986960000473794, \"rank\": 0.0013056943257172245, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Ramos spike deflected off Wilkerson's hands and the celebration was on for hundreds of vocal Brazilian supporters.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2808, \"end\": 2813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\", \"score\": 0.9999999714405026, \"rank\": 2.338120157056417e-08, \"text\": \"Ramos\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was Brazil's first women's gold since the Atlanta Games.\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2930, \"end\": 2936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9986960000473794, \"rank\": 0.0013056943257172245, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are fighting for the same thing,\\\" Wilkerson said.\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is only one gold medal and there is two teams going for it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The seventh-ranked Humana-Paredes and Wilkerson reached the final after a comeback victory a day earlier against Tanja Hueberli and Nina Brunner of Switzerland.\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3126, \"end\": 3140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Humana-Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\"}, {\"begin\": 3255, \"end\": 3266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9982449670388576, \"rank\": 0.0016772291301088732, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They saved a match ball in the three-set semifinal win.\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top-ranked Brazilians also beat the Canadians in a tightly contested Pan Am Games final last year in Santiago, Chile.\", \"from\": 3325, \"to\": 3446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3340, \"end\": 3350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999031388, \"rank\": 9.706457098100313e-11, \"text\": \"Brazilians\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3430, \"end\": 3438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"score\": 0.9999968290999528, \"rank\": 3.1490773667814403e-06, \"text\": \"Santiago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\"}, {\"begin\": 3440, \"end\": 3445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997181521274184, \"rank\": 0.00028152091899989127, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier Friday, Hueberli and Brunner defeated Australia's Taliqua Clancy and Mariafe Artacho del Solar 21-17, 21-15 for the bronze medal.\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3494, \"end\": 3503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9995638623261638, \"rank\": 0.00029866999313623953, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3506, \"end\": 3520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliqua_Clancy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taliqua Clancy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliqua_Clancy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliqua_Clancy\"}, {\"begin\": 3525, \"end\": 3550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariafe_Artacho_del_Solar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mariafe Artacho del Solar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariafe_Artacho_del_Solar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariafe_Artacho_del_Solar\"}, {\"begin\": 3533, \"end\": 3550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariafe_Artacho_del_Solar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Artacho del Solar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariafe_Artacho_del_Solar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariafe_Artacho_del_Solar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's medal matches were scheduled for Saturday.\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3639, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sweden was to play Germany for gold and Norway was to face Qatar for bronze.\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3640, \"end\": 3646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.8326887067113315, \"rank\": 0.19226052218278689, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3659, \"end\": 3666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.844018585756871, \"rank\": 0.18480803251748396, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3680, \"end\": 3686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9931506513121497, \"rank\": 0.006896568038027697, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3699, \"end\": 3704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999778320847235, \"rank\": 0.0002217232864425884, \"text\": \"Qatar\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This report by The Canadian Press was first published Aug. 9, 2024.\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3733, \"end\": 3751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canadian_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Canadian Press\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canadian_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canadian_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 3737, \"end\": 3751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canadian_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canadian Press\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.or